							<p>Our Career Development program is dedicated to supporting students in achieving their professional goals. Through personalized career counseling, we provide one-on-one guidance to help students explore various career options, refine their career aspirations, and develop actionable plans. Our experienced career counselors are committed to helping you navigate the complexities of career planning and decision-making.</p><p>We offer a range of services to ensure students gain valuable experience and are well-prepared for the job market. Internship opportunities are available across various industries, providing practical experience and helping students build professional networks. Our job placement services support students with job searching, resume writing, and interview preparation, ensuring they are competitive candidates in their chosen fields.</p><p>To further enhance career readiness, we host workshops and events such as resume and cover letter workshops, interview preparation sessions, and career fairs. These events are designed to equip students with the necessary skills and connections for career success. Additionally, we facilitate networking opportunities with alumni and industry professionals, helping students build a robust professional network. For more details or to schedule an appointment with a career counselor, please contact us via email or phone.</p>						</div>
